---
---

<section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center radial-glow pt-20">
  <!-- Decorative elements -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-purple/5 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-float"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-cyan/5 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-float" style="animation-delay: -3s;"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 text-center">
    <div class="animate-fade-in-up">
      <div class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-purple/30 bg-purple/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm text-purple-light">
        <span class="inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-cyan animate-pulse"></span>
        Growth Consulting + AI Automation
      </div>
    </div>

    <h1 class="animate-fade-in-up delay-100 text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
      Escala tu empresa tech<br />
      <span class="gradient-text">sin escalar tu equipo</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="animate-fade-in-up delay-200 mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-gray-400 leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
      Construyo sistemas de growth y automatizaciones con IA que eliminan cuellos de botella,
      aceleran tu pipeline y te hacen crecer de forma predecible.
    </p>

    <div class="animate-fade-in-up delay-300 mt-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center">
      <a
        href="#contacto"
        class="group rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-purple to-cyan px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-purple/25 hover:scale-105"
      >
        Agenda una llamada
        <span class="inline-block transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">&rarr;</span>
      </a>
      <a
        href="#proceso"
        class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-medium text-gray-300 transition-all hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-white/20"
      >
        Ver proceso
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <div class="animate-fade-in-up delay-500 mt-20 grid grid-cols-3 gap-8 border-t border-white/5 pt-10">
      <div>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold gradient-text">+50</div>
        <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500">Proyectos de growth</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold gradient-text">3x</div>
        <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500">Pipeline promedio</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold gradient-text">-70%</div>
        <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500">Tiempo operativo</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
